Title: Mum
Plot: Vic struggles with Claudette's new supervision of the Strike Team.  Marked bills lead Aceveda and a federal agent closer to the truth about the Armenian money-train heist in an episode with a recurring motif of people not reporting crimes against them.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence,sexual violence and offensive language
GuestStars: David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Michele Hicks, Lyne Odums, Peggy Miley, Kurt Caceres, Afemo Omilami, Vincent Angell, Andrew Borba
